---
/**
 * Balloon-letter overlay for a .phero page heading — mirrors the home hero's
 * canvas. JS (balloons.ts) reads the sibling <h1 class="phero__title"> and mounts
 * here; the real <h1> stays the accessible/SEO source of truth, so this canvas is
 * aria-hidden. The replay button lives in the header. Drop inside a `.phero`
 * section (it's position:relative).
 */
---

<canvas class="phero__canvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
